{"tid":1764020,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"跪求大家在121尖沙咀大遊行的遊行時段內，必須百份百和理非","createTime":"2019-11-30T19:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T20:30:10.000Z","uid":12773,"like":25,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8e16776ffbb207460ce2cb2500276efc2123652c","tid":1764020,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:34:12.000Z","msg":"眾所周知<br />\n今次遊行係由一名冇政黨背景，冇幕後金主<br />\n用自己個人名義<br />\n入紙不反對通知書的連登素人主辧<br />\n亦由眾多連登仔<br />\n前後花了五日合全力協辦<br />\n成個story 如下<br />\n<br />\n可能係第一位素人連登仔主辦的九龍大遊行，大家唔會唔撐掛！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1761277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1761277</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果在今次遊行時段內有乜衣郁<br />\n主辦人因以個人名義<br />\n入紙申請不反對通知書<br />\n好有可能被告煽動暴動<br />\n所以跪求各手足<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在遊行時段內</span><br />\n盡量忍耐<br />\n保持百份百和理非之心去參與<br />\n勿受任何惡毒邪魔挑釁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n況且如果今次大遊行可以順順利利<br />\n則標誌着以往依靠政黨申請大遊行的時代<br />\n已告終結<br />\n任何素人都可以起義<br />\n任何素人都可以申辦遊行<br />\n香港抗爭之路<br />\n亦邁上新一頁<br />\n<br />\n如同意<br />\n請推上熱門<br />\n及分發此post比身邊所有人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區選雖勝<br />\n毋忘初心<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n決一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiyeSNh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiiyeSNh.jpg&h=214ecbc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CjeBmFD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjeBmFD.jpg&h=465958e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bYgToTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbYgToTY.jpg&h=67844e8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4b79ad6c56e961b837b7dbf7355d43e70129b2d","tid":1764020,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0029cb704098f7a78109121d72322800a8dcc05","tid":1764020,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b06d86fa771785f422f137b45d86ec411e4d8f","tid":1764020,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hk